TitMainTitle: Group portrait of sixteen women, some Westinghouse High School students, including Caroline Bush and Alvinia Holt seated on floor, with Evelyn Allsberry and Deola Hartwell standing third and second on right, posed in living room with framed '54 Champs W [Westinghouse High School] varsity letters on wall in background, possibly in home at 4035 Monticello Street, Homewood
